*******************************
BDR(Backup & disaster recovery)
*******************************
>Recover data from snapshot only

>select snapshot

>Select action tab

>Create volume from snapshot

>Attach that volume to EC2 instance

>Connect to EC2 instance 

>Take control

>Check whether volume is attached
# lsblk

> Chek if there is any data on volume
# file -s /dev/xvdf

>Mount HDD
#sudo mount /dev/xvdf /fileserver

#cd /fileserver

>check backup done or not
ls

